* component contains
    cd4Result 1..1 and
    cd4Percentage 1..1
* component[cd4Result].code = $SCT#113056008 "CD4 result"
* component[cd4Result].valueInteger 1..1
* component[cd4Percentage].code = $SCT#313938009 "CD4 percentage"
* component[cd4Percentage].valueInteger 1..1

